result.title: tamrine serie panjom
result.content:
salam
tamrine in haftatun ro mitunin az inja bebinin. vase in hafte faghat soale 534o accept konin kafie vali chan ta soale khube dige ham az ide haii ke sare kelas gofte shode gozashtam ke age khastin bahashun dargir shin dige ^.^.
deghat konin ke soala kheyli sakhtan va bar asase sakhti vase man moratab shodan.
age betunin 2 ya 3ta accept dashte bashin kheyli alie vali khob age hichi ham accept nakardin na omid nashin chon in soala kheyli sakhtan

mo'afagh bashin :)
